metadata.description: Message To Martians Characters are your core avatars in the MTM Ecosystem. A maximum of 8888 will exist - but far less will remain after Augmentation.  A character can be minted with a Transponder and Space Capsule pair, you can learn more and check your redemption status for a Character at www.messagetomartians.com.
